{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"elyse holladay","author":"Elyse Holladay Cherewaty"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e66db034-eedf-5f92-a480-7cecdb110672","html":"<p>Design Systems are our current model of making sense of the intersection of front-end code and design. With the tools we have today, what is our working model of a component? How do we define them, create them, and ensure they work at scale? In this talk weâ€™ll discuss how our tools affect our understanding, create a checklist of factors that make a component a component, and how to implement the theory of components with the tools you have at hand.</p>\n<p><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"slides 1\" title=\"\" src=\"/static/5905f32ca8f8feb89f98a4ec53ba287f/ca545/slides-1.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/5905f32ca8f8feb89f98a4ec53ba287f/aa1b7/slides-1.jpg 148w,\n/static/5905f32ca8f8feb89f98a4ec53ba287f/b937a/slides-1.jpg 295w,\n/static/5905f32ca8f8feb89f98a4ec53ba287f/ca545/slides-1.jpg 590w,\n/static/5905f32ca8f8feb89f98a4ec53ba287f/75639/slides-1.jpg 885w,\n/static/5905f32ca8f8feb89f98a4ec53ba287f/8bd51/slides-1.jpg 1180w,\n/static/5905f32ca8f8feb89f98a4ec53ba287f/a3716/slides-1.jpg 1770w,\n/static/5905f32ca8f8feb89f98a4ec53ba287f/6b37f/slides-1.jpg 4000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\">\n  </span></p>\n<p><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">\n    <span class